title: #92Noon! Nordo in for PA! Friday Football Feast!
description:
Eric Nordquist is in the big chair for PA! Voice of the Gophers Mike Grimm joins ahead of the big game against Michigan on Saturday. Your 5 Predictions.
A visit from Chad Greenway and his thoughts on this current Vikings season. Some news with Brianne. 
And Ron Johnson joins in studio to talk a "grown man football team."
